# Mobile Development Rules Index

**Purpose**: Router for mobile rules - detects keywords and routes to language indexes or platform files.

**Chaining**: Root Router → This Index (Router) → Language Index → Files

**Graph Structure**: This is a Layer 2 node that routes to Layer 2 nodes (language indexes) based on keywords.

**Hybrid Routing**: All mobile languages are flattened - language indexes route directly to files (2 hops total).

