## Loading Pattern

**Router → This Index → Language Router/Index → Platform/Subcategory Index → Files**

1. Root Router detects "mobile" or platform keyword → loads this index
2. This index routes to language router/index or platform file
3. Language router/index routes to subcategory indexes
4. Subcategory indexes point to specific rule files

